</div>
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_124_r1l20">Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> VVir bıten ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mit <expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiſʒ / daʒ ewr gnade </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_124_r1l21">vnſer <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> vnd kaufflewte vnd auch Jr habe vnd <expan>kauffmanſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> </ab>
