<ab facs="#facs_124_r1l25">oder die Jren / darümb cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden oder aber den ~ <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> kumen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_124_r1l26">vnd des begern / daʒ ſie vnd das Jr <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> lande herſchaft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_124_r1l27">vnd gepiete ſicher geleẏtet werden / Als etc das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_124_r1l28">biten auch des <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnedig <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wider beẏ diſem <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_124_r1l30">diener / <expan>Sc<ex>ri</ex>pt<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vj̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
